Tiger Woods, facing a race to be fit after back spasms brought an early end to his tournament at Firestone, is set to join fellow American Phil Mickelson and Dubliner Padraig Harrington in one of the early groups on day one.

Defending champion Jason Dufner, partnering YE Yang and Keegan Bradley, is in the group following McIlroy, Watson and Kaymer.

